body( data-spy = "scroll", data-target = ".bs-docs-sidebar" )
  include docs-nav.html

  header.jumbotron.subhead#overview
    div.container
      h1 Components
      p Basic UI Components, with examples.

  div.container

    div.bs-docs-sidebar
      ul.simple-nav.nav-list.bs-docs-sidenav
        li
          a(href='#carousels')
            i.icon-chevron-right
            | Carousels

    div.bs-docs-main-content
      section#carousels
        h2#headings Carousels
        p
          | The&nbsp;
          code
            | SonyCarousel
          |  class creates a number of carousel variations. "sony-carousel" classes (see Jade example below) provide
          | basic styles, and are used throughout this page, but you may create your own implementation of the CSS
          | so long as:

        ol
          li The carousel wrapper (.sony-carousel-wrapper in examples) is overflow: hidden; and is position: relative/absolute;
          li The carousel slider (.sony-carousel in examples) contains all the slides (.sony-carousel-slides in examples)
            | from left to right, whether by absolute/relative positioning or floats. (Though should at least be position: relative;)
          li If you're making a looped carousel, your CSS should allow for items to be dynamically added
            | on both ends of the carousel without breaking the layout.

        p More detailed documentation of the Javascript class is located
          a(href="docco/secondary/sony-carousel.html")  here.

        h4 Example (Jade)

        pre.prettyprint.prettyprint-jade
          |   div#carousel-(number)
          |     div.sony-carousel-wrapper
          |       div.sony-carousel
          |         div.sony-carousel-slide
          |           div.sony-carousel-slide-children
          |           div.sony-carousel-slide-children
          |         div.sony-carousel-slide
          |           div.sony-carousel-slide-children
          |           div.sony-carousel-slide-children
          |         div.carousel-slide
          |           div.sony-carousel-slide-children
          |           div.sony-carousel-slide-children

